correctness.rationale: Several key fields are inaccurate, not traceable to the article, or internally inconsistent, despite some correct high-level entries (PEALD of ZnO with DMZ and O2, Ar carrier = 15 sccm, O2 = 80 sccm, plasma power 100 W, pressure 400 mTorr, Si substrates, ~80 nm films). Major issues: (1) Dosing/purge times are incorrectly interpreted: DMZ exposure values (75–125 mTorr·s) were converted to milliseconds. Plasma exposure is 2 s (should be 2000 ms to fit schema), but extraction uses 2 ms. Purge is 10 s (should be 10000 ms), extraction uses 10 ms. (2) Number of cycles (1000) is not supported: with GPC 1.6 Å/cycle at 25 C, 80 nm would require ~500 cycles; 1000 cycles would yield ~160 nm. (3) Resistivity unit/value mismatch: article reports 270 ohm-cm at RT; encoded as 270 OHM-M, which should be 2.7 OHM-M if using that unit. (4) Many properties are unreported in the paper but filled with placeholders or fabricated values: carrierDensity (1e18 m^-3; not reported and unit off by 1e6 if meant cm^-3), bandGap (3.3 eV; not reported), uniformity variation (0%), conformality aspect ratio (0), elementalConcentration (0%), filmDensity (5.6 g/dm^3; not measured and unit implies 0.0056 g/cm^3), nucleationPeriod (0 cycles; not reported). These should be omitted or clearly not provided per schema, not set to zero. (5) Film composition/ratio inconsistent with chosen temperature: atomicRatio 1:1 is supported only within the ALD window or after sputter at 120 C; at 25 C films show OH/carbon and O/Zn ~1.1–1.2. (6) Refractive index 2.0 corresponds to ALD window; at 25 C it is lower (Fig. 4); update to temperature-consistent value or cite the appropriate temperature. (7) DeviceProperties are not applicable; the paper does not report TFT metrics (field-effect mobility, Vth, SS, on/off). Using Hall mobility (~1 cm^2/Vs) under deviceProperties is incorrect. (8) FlowRates: precursorFlow 15 sccm is the Ar carrier through the bubbler, not the DMZ molar flow; label this explicitly or move to carrier/purge gas context. Corrections should focus on fixing dosing/purge times and units, adjusting number of cycles to match thickness and GPC, correcting resistivity units, removing or marking as not reported the unsubstantiated properties (band gap, carrier density, device properties, uniformity, conformality, film density, elemental concentration), and ensuring film composition and refractive index are consistent with the selected deposition temperature.

completeness.rationale: Substantial incompleteness and inconsistency vs. the article and schema. (1) Multiple processes not represented: the paper reports many depositions across 25–120 °C and varying DMZ exposure; only one process (25 °C) is extracted. (2) Key time/units errors: plasma (co-reactant) exposure should be ~2 s but is recorded as 2 ms; purge times should be 10 s but are 10 ms; precursor dosing time (75 ms) is not reported in the paper (exposures were given in mTorr·s). (3) Electrical units/values wrong: resistivity is reported as 270 Ω·cm at RT but extracted as 270 Ω·m; carrier density value and unit (1e18 m⁻³) are not reported and unit is inconsistent with common cm⁻³ in the paper; mobility given as a fixed 1 cm²/V·s despite noted variability. (4) Thickness control inconsistent: numberofCycles = 1000 conflicts with 80 nm film thickness and GPC 1.6 Å/cycle (would imply ~500 cycles for 80 nm); growth-per-cycle at 25 °C is OK, but refractive index = 2.0 corresponds to ALD window films, not 25 °C. (5) Composition mismatch: atomic ratio set to 1:1 while room-temperature films are oxygen-rich (O/Zn ~1.1–1.2); elemental concentration “0%” is unphysical and not reported. (6) Added unreported properties: band gap (3.3 eV), absorption coefficient (0), uniformity (0%), conformality aspect ratio (0), film density with wrong unit (g/dm³ instead of g/cm³) and implausible method (ellipsometry), device properties (μ_FE, V_TH, SS, I_ON/I_OFF) are not in the article. (7) Flow rates: 15 sccm is Ar carrier, not DMZ molecular flow; mapping as precursorFlow is ambiguous. (8) NucleationPeriod set to 0 without support. (9) Delivery method is actually described (bubbler with Ar carrier, continuous O2) but marked “Not Found.” Properties to add/review: represent separate processes for key temperatures (e.g., 25 °C, ~57 °C, ≥85–120 °C) with coherent GPC, RI, resistivity; correct units and magnitudes for resistivity (Ω·cm), times (seconds), and film density (g/cm³) or omit if not measured; replace precursor/co-reactant dosing and purge times with traceable values (2 s plasma, 10 s purges) and avoid inventing precursor dose time; correct atomic ratio per temperature; remove unreported device and optical parameters; align numberofCycles with GPC and film thickness; clarify delivery method and map flow rates to carrier/purging gas explicitly.
